<h1>Passage</h1>
a video game by <a href="http://hcsoftware.sf.net/jason-rohrer">Jason Rohrer</a><br>
<br>

<font size=5>[try Jason Rohrer's latest game <a href="http://sleepisdeath.net">Sleep Is Death</a>]</font>

<!--[to read about more art games, checkout <a href="http://northcountrynotes.org/jason-rohrer/arthouseGames">Arthouse Games</a>]-->
</center>
<br>
<br>
This was selected for exhibition at <a href="http://kokoromi.org/projects/gamma256">Kokoromi's Gamma256</a> event.<br>
<br>
